Features:
  1. characters
  2. frequency
  
Solution:
  1. use Counter to calculate the first word about the times of each character
  2. take intersection of all words' Counter one by one
  3. transform the final intersection dictionary into a list
      
Notes:
  1. collections.Counter(word):
      key: characters
      value: times of characters
  2. the way to take intersection of dictionaries:
      1. dic1 & dic2
      2. dic[k] = min(dic1[k], dic2[k])
  
